@startuml
actor "User" as User
participant "Web Frontend" as Frontend
participant "API Gateway\n(Kong)" as Kong
participant "Conversation Service" as ConversationService
database "Conversation DB" as ConversationDB
participant "LiveKit SDK" as LiveKitSDK
participant "LiveKit Cloud" as LiveKit

== Luồng nghiệp vụ: Cấp token voice chat qua LiveKit ==

User -> Frontend: Bấm bắt đầu đàm thoại bằng giọng nói
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Kong: GET /code-conversation-service/chats/{chat_id}/voice-token\n?file_ids={doc_ids}&use_reasoning=true&persona_id={persona_id}
activate Kong
Kong -> ConversationService: Chuyển tiếp yêu cầu lấy voice token
activate ConversationService

opt ENVIRONMENT != development
ConversationService -> ConversationDB: isVip(userId)\ntrong user_subscriptions
activate ConversationDB
ConversationDB --> ConversationService: true nếu subscription còn hiệu lực
deactivate ConversationDB
end

alt #F2F4F7 User không có VIP hợp lệ
ConversationService --> Kong: ForbiddenException
Kong --> Frontend: HTTP 403
Frontend --> User: Hiển thị yêu cầu nâng cấp VIP
else Được phép cấp token
ConversationService -> LiveKitSDK: Tạo AccessToken\nmetadata={chat_id,user_id,file_ids,use_reasoning,persona_id}
activate LiveKitSDK
LiveKitSDK --> ConversationService: JWT có roomJoin, canPublish,\ncanSubscribe, canUpdateOwnMetadata
deactivate LiveKitSDK

ConversationService --> Kong: HTTP 200 { token, serverUrl }
deactivate ConversationService
Kong --> Frontend: Trả token và LIVEKIT_URL
deactivate Kong

Frontend -> LiveKit: Join room chat_id bằng token
activate LiveKit
LiveKit --> Frontend: Join room thành công
deactivate LiveKit

Frontend --> User: Mở phiên voice chat
end

deactivate Frontend
@enduml
